Summary: 1 large red light,1smaller seperating orange light ,then 4 seperating lights
divs: Sighting Details I was walking north by a baseball park,happened to look right and up for Jupiter,below,saw bright red object then a smaller orange one seperating up and to the right of first object. they appeared to be in a right bank, like aircraft. Discounting aircraft,having worked on the flight-line for 20 yrs. lights of this color and brightness dont just appear on a clear night with out some sort of an approach.These 2 lights ejected 4 smaller ones to the left and down. Something similar to a Citation 5 in a right bank. This lasted 4-5 secs.then vanished.I scanned a couple seconds and these lights reappeared in the same line fashion for a couple more seconds,then vanished.I know this is something I will forever remember. And, I have faith in the believers.
